SEOChecker.cc 是一个高效易用的浏览器扩展程序，专为热爱 SEO 和网站流量增长的用户设计。仅需一键，您就可以快捷查询到当前浏览网站的全面 SEO 数据，包括但不限于 Google、Bing 和 Baidu 等主流搜索引擎的网站收录数量，还有 SimilarWeb 提供的流量分析，以及 Whois 的详细域名信息。此外，我们还精选了一系列业内优秀的 SEO 工具，帮助您更全面地优化网站。

产品反馈请联系 hi@copilotbase.com

SEOChecker.cc is an efficient and user-friendly browser extension, designed specifically for those passionate about SEO and website traffic growth. With just a single click, you can quickly access comprehensive SEO data of the website you're currently browsing. This includes but is not limited to the site's index count on mainstream search engines like Google, Bing, and Baidu, as well as traffic analytics from SimilarWeb and detailed domain information from Whois. Additionally, we have handpicked a series of industry-leading SEO tools to help you optimize your website more holistically.

Contact us: hi@copilotbase.com
